Actions.Text: REFERRED TO TOURISM, PARKS, ARTS AND SPORTS DEVELOPMENT

Title: Requires members of a boat club complete a boating safety course
Summary: Requires owners, operators, employees, customers and persons using a boat club shall successfully complete a boating safety course.
LawCode: Add ยง398-g, Gen Bus L
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the general business law, in relation to requiring members of a boat club complete a boating safety course
